description:
On today’s show, Emily is giving you ways to get out of your head and into your sexual groove.

She reveals why being a perfectionist may be stopping you from having the sex you want and how to get over insecurities about your penis size – whether it’s big, small, or somewhere in between. Plus, what to do if you’re craving more affection from your partner and tips to start your masturbation routine off right.
